 "remarks": "Sun-filled Colonial set on 2 private acres with desirable east/west exposures, offering exceptional privacy and natural beauty. Thoughtfully updated throughout, the home features a renovated gourmet kitchen with premium appliances, breakfast area, and seamless connection to the family room. French doors open to a terraced deck overlooking lush grounds, mature landscaping, a charming bridge, and tranquil lush green views. The second floor offers four bdrms including a spacious primary suite with luxury bath, dressing area, and custom closets.The finished walkout lower level with full bath provides flexible space for guests, recreation, home office, gym, nanny, or in-law suite. Recent improvements include Andersen windows and doors, generator, updated mechanicals, irrigation, security system and more!",
